Amazon DSP: Audio and video report grouped by content
Audio and video reports
Audio and video reports contain data based on content genre and content rating.

Configurations
Configuration	Amazon DSP
reportTypeId	dspAudioAndVideo
Maximum date range	395 days
Data retention	395 days
timeUnit	SUMMARY
groupBy	campaign, ad, supplySource, creative, content
format	GZIP_JSON, XLSX, or CSV
Amazon DSP
Base metrics
intervalStart, intervalEnd, advertiserName, advertiserId, impressions, grossImpressions, invalidImpressions, costPerThousandImpressions

Group by campaign
Additional metrics: orderName, orderId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by ad
Additional metrics: lineItemName, lineItemId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by creative
Additional metrics: creativeName, creativeId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by supplySource
Additional metrics: supplySource, supplySourceId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by content
Additional metrics: contentGenre, contentRating, contentTitle, contentType

Filters: advertiserId

Sample calls
Amazon DSP: Audio and video report grouped by content
curl --location 'https://advertising-api.amazon.com/reporting/reports' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/vnd.createasyncreportrequest.v3+json' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-ClientId: amzn1.application-oa2-client.xxxxxxx' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-Scope: xxxxxxxxxxx' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer Atza|xxxxxxx' \
--data '{
    "name":"dsp 7/5-7/10",
    "startDate":"2024-02-05",
    "endDate":"2024-02-10",
    "configuration":{
        "adProduct": "DEMAND_SIDE_PLATFORM",
        "columns": ["contentGenre"],
        "format": "CSV",
        "reportTypeId": "dspAudioAndVideo",
        "groupBy": [
            "content"
        ],
        "filters": [{"field":"advertiserId","values":["xxxxxxxxxx"]}],
        "timeUnit": "SUMMARY"
    }
}'
