Sample requests
Amazon DSP: Brand suitability report grouped by inventoryTier
Amazon DSP: Brand suitability report grouped by contentCategory
Brand suitability reports
Brand suitability gives you control over where your ads appear based on your brand's values and risk tolerance. You can customize these controls at the advertiser and line item level.

Configurations
Configuration	Amazon DSP
reportTypeId	dspBrandSuitability
Maximum date range	395 days
Data retention	395 days
timeUnit	SUMMARY or DAILY
groupBy	campaign, ad, supplySource, inventoryTier, contentCategory
format	GZIP_JSON, CSV, or XLSX
Amazon DSP
Base metrics
intervalStart, intervalEnd, advertiserName, advertiserId, impressions

Group by campaign
Additional metrics: orderName, orderId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by ad
Additional metrics: lineItemName, lineItemId

Filters: advertiserId

Group by supplySource
Additional metrics: supplySource,

Filters: advertiserId

Group by inventoryTier
Additional metrics: inventoryTier

Filters: advertiserId

Group by contentCategory
Additional metrics: contentCategory

Filters: advertiserId

[!IMPORTANT] The report request cannot include both contentCategory and inventoryTier dimensions simultaneously. Please choose only one of these dimensions in your groupBy parameter: Use contentCategory OR Use inventoryTier.
Sample requests
Amazon DSP: Brand suitability report grouped by inventoryTier
curl --location 'https://advertising-api.amazon.com/reporting/reports' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/vnd.createasyncreportrequest.v3+json' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-ClientId: amzn1.application-oa2-client.xxxxxxx' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-Scope: xxxxxxxxxxx' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer Atza|xxxxxxx' \
--data '{
    "name":"dsp 9/5-9/10",
    "startDate":"2025-09-10",
    "endDate":"2025-09-15",
    "configuration":{
        "adProduct": "DEMAND_SIDE_PLATFORM",
        "columns": ["inventoryTier"],
        "format": "CSV",
        "reportTypeId": "dspBrandSuitability",
        "groupBy": [
            "inventoryTier"
        ],
        "filters": [{"field":"advertiserId","values":["xxxxxxxxxx"]}],
        "timeUnit": "SUMMARY"
    }
}'
Amazon DSP: Brand suitability report grouped by contentCategory
curl --location 'https://advertising-api.amazon.com/reporting/reports' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/vnd.createasyncreportrequest.v3+json' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-ClientId: amzn1.application-oa2-client.xxxxxxx' \
--header 'Amazon-Advertising-API-Scope: xxxxxxxxxxx' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer Atza|xxxxxxx' \
--data '{
    "name":"dsp brand suitability by content category",
    "startDate":"2025-09-10",
    "endDate":"2025-09-15",
    "configuration":{
        "adProduct": "DEMAND_SIDE_PLATFORM",
        "columns": ["contentCategory"],
        "format": "CSV",
        "reportTypeId": "dspBrandSuitability",
        "groupBy": [
            "contentCategory"
        ],
        "filters": [{"field":"advertiserId","values":["xxxxxxxxxx"]}],
        "timeUnit": "SUMMARY"
    }
}'
